  "A Ferris wheel has a radius of 20 meters, its center is 25 meters above the ground, and it completes one revolution every 40 seconds. A rider boards at the lowest point. Which function models the rider's height h(t) in meters after t seconds?": "",
  "h(t) = -20 sin(pi*t/20) + 25": "",
