  "A rescue helicopter spots a stranded hiker. The helicopter is at an altitude of 300 meters and observes the hiker at an angle of depression of 40 degrees. How far must the helicopter travel horizontally to be directly above the hiker? (Use tan(40) = 0.839.)": "",
