  "Approximately 357.6 meters": "",
  "Approximately 466.3 meters": "",
  "Approximately 251.7 meters": "",
  "The angle of depression equals the angle of elevation from the hiker. tan(40) = 300/d, so d = 300/tan(40) = 300/0.839 approximately equals 357.6 meters.": "",
  "A student is asked to find all solutions of 2 cos^2(x) - cos(x) - 1 = 0 on [0, 2pi). Factoring gives (2 cos(x) + 1)(cos(x) - 1) = 0. How many solutions exist?": "",
